description: Capacent Holding AB engages in the provision of consulting services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 79 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-10-02. The Firm provides management consultancy services that focus on improving its customer's profitability and cash flow. Its servces include company wide programs, finance and performance management, operations management, market and customer managements, pricing and revenue management, and information and digital transformation. Its customers include outokumpu, PEAB, Uddeholm, SJ, tokmanni and Martela, among others.
naics: Management, Scientific, and Technical Consulting Services
